Audio to Notes Web App
This Next.js web application provides an aesthetic interface for users to upload audio files, convert them into text using the Gemini 2.5 Flash API, and elegantly represent the output as organized notes.

User Review Required
Framework: We plan to use Next.js (App Router) combined with pure Vanilla CSS, ensuring a high-performance, single-project full-stack application. Is Next.js acceptable to you?
Aesthetic: We'll implement a minimalist, premium glassmorphic dark mode design, utilizing modern web fonts (e.g. Inter). No Tailwind CSS will be used according to system rules unless overridden.
Environment Route: The Gemini API Key must be supplied in a .env.local file GEMINI_API_KEY=YOUR_KEY since API requests will be securely routed through Next.js server actions / API endpoints to avoid exposing it to the frontend.
