Backend Generation (API)
[NEW] src/app/api/transcribe/route.ts
Accepts a FormData payload containing the audio file.
Converts it to a temporary file.
Uploads the audio file using the Gemini API googleGenai.files.upload.
Calls models.generateContent on gemini-2.5-flash with the audio and a prompt customized for audio summarization and note-taking.
Deletes the remote file after returning the response, returning a markdown string to the client.
